{"parse":{"title":"Zulian Mudskunk","pageid":60748,"wikitext":{"*":"__NOTOC__\n<onlyinclude>{{tooltip\n|mode={{{mode|}}}\n|arg={{{arg|}}}\n|icon=INV_Misc_Fish_05\n|quality=Common\n|itemid=19975\n|ilvl=1\n|name=Zulian Mudskunk}}</onlyinclude> \n\n\nThe '''Zulian Mudskunk''' is a fish found only in the waters of [[Zul'Gurub]]. These fish are a favorite of the water beast [[Gahz'ranka]] and can be used to pull him from his lair.\n{{clrl}}\n== Source ==\nThese fish can be pulled from the waters in Zul'Gurub. The best place to find them are at [[Muddy Churning Water]] spots. It requires a fishing skill of 350 to land the fish.\n\n== Notes ==\n*This item stacks in groups of 20.\n*You need 5 Zulian Mudskunks and a [[Mudskunk Lure]] to summon Gahz'ranka. He can only be summoned once per instance.\n*This could also be obtained by killing toads in Darnassus. //Jeroro//\n\n==Patches and hotfixes==\n{{Patch 1.7.0|note=Added}}\n\n==External links==\n<!-- Read http://www.wowwiki.com/WoWWiki:External_links before posting your links here.\nLinks that do not conform to the rules will be DELETED.\nRepeat violations may result in a BAN.\nHave a nice day. :) -->\n{{elinks-item|19975}}\n{{Elink|link=http://www.elsanglin.com/fish/zulian_mudskunk.html |site=El's Extreme Anglin' |icon=elsanglin}}\n\n\n[[Category:World of Warcraft common fished items]]\n[[Category:Zul'Gurub items]]"}}}